name: 092 Destruction
description:
A falling rectangle,
Like a long time ago,
So many lives leaving, I think
So much madness that guides the steps of madmen
To simply invade a country.

A rectangle,
Which falls and many lives facing the TVs, facing the news,
having dreams that hurt us.
And these links that we could make between us...

And then the wars that we thought so far away,
Far from the luxury of our rectangles, which vibrate in our pockets.
To warn us once more that everything is wrong,
Fallen to the ground,
 I only want to make the world a better place.

That's all
